参加《Vtuber甲子园》的成员概要 超越团体和公司的界限，人气VTuber出现在游戏中【2月19日新增】 https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-koshien-2024-member/ノンジャンル人生 Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:58:02 +0000 VTuberVTuber甲子園 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=245906 <p> “Vtuber甲子园”是受欢迎的VTuber超越团体和公司的界限，参加现场强大的职业棒球比赛的地方。各队均已开始队伍培养，一年级球员也已到来。 “Vtuber Koshien”是 VTuber 进行 eBA 的地方 […]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-koshien-2024-member/">参与“Vtuber甲子园”的成员的帖子摘要 受欢迎的VTuber超越团体和公司的界限，出现在游戏中[2月19日添加]</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>受欢迎的 VTuber 超越团体和公司的界限，参加现场强大的职业棒球比赛的<strong>“Vtuber 甲子园”</strong> 。各队均已开始队伍培养，一年级球员也已到来。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1p879895pt4j-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> “Vtuber甲子园”是VTuber们与<a href="https://www.konami.com/pawa/2022/powerful" target="_blank" rel="noopener">eBASEBALL强力职业棒球2022</a> （2023更新版）的Eikon九人组创建的队伍相互竞争的项目。这次， <a href="https://neo-porte.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Neo-Porte</strong></a>的<a href="https://twitter.com/ShibuyaHAL" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>涉谷晴</strong></a>、虹山寺的<a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>椎名由香</strong></a>、 <a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hololive</strong></a><a href="https://twitter.com/hakuikoyori" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>的</strong></a><a href="https://twitter.com/yuika_siina" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>小赖广井</strong></a>、Individuals 的<a href="https://twitter.com/tenkaitukasa" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>天海司</strong></a>将作为导演参与。</p><p>在永观九号开始时，六名新学生将加入，每个人都能够创建自己的角色。一些转世的职业棒球运动员甚至加入了俱乐部。然而，在Vtuber甲子园中，有一个规则，你只能在开始时重置游戏两次，所以你能否组建你的理想团队很大程度上取决于运气。当球队在第三年夏天完成时，看看每所高中都会聚集什么样的成员将会很有趣。</p><p> *2 月 19 日添加：所有团队的二年级成员均已列出。</p><h2>霍洛莱夫高中</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.1y6ywe6rt8jx-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>导演: 广井小赖</p><p>[第一年]<br />・宝翔马琳（投手）<br />・白神吹雪（投手）<br />・佐仓巫女（捕手）<br />・拉普拉斯·达克尼斯（外野手）<br />・百鬼彩女（外野手）<br />・时之空（外野手）</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/40104bf3f5bb01502057e87fa36b5177-kix.tvp2g3n8snpy-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> [第2年]<br />・关华·拉米（三垒手